### Meskalina ###
{:#Meskalina}

Café bar [Meskalina](http://www.meskalina.com) will host the *TypeShorts* evening.
Located in a modernist building of the Arsenal Gallery in the middle of the Old Market, 
Mescalina is a place of many cultural events. Continuing the tradition of its older brother, 
Meskal, it became one of the most favorite Poznań artistic clubs. There is always something going on.
The restaurant can accommodate around 150 people and during the summer opens its beer garden with a music stage.

